<h1 style="margin-top:40px">Primer Search v0.01</h1>
<h3>Author: Chad Stachowicz (cstachowicz@cloverhound.com)</h3>
<p>You can use this small application to search for primers for PCR in a sequence of your choice</p>
<p>***NOTE*** I did this as an expirment myself, do not order these primers without checking them youself.</p>
<a href="https://twitter.com/chadstachowicz">Twitter</a>
<br/>
<form method="POST" action="/results">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="sequence" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Sequence to search</label>
      <textarea class="form-control" id="sequence" name="sequence" rows="10"></textarea>
  </div><br/>
  <h5>Melting Temperature Range (Tm)</h5>
  <div class="form-group row">
    <label for="minTm" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Min Tm</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="minTm" name="minTm" value="40">
    </div>
    <label for="maxTm" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Min Tm</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="maxTm" name="maxTm" value="60">
    </div>
  </div><br/>
  <h5>GC Content Range (GC)</h5>
  <div class="form-group row">
    <label for="minGc" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Min GC</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="minGc" name="minGc" value="50">
    </div>
    <label for="maxGc" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Max GC</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="maxGc" name="maxGc" value="60">
    </div>
  </div><br/>
  <h5>Primer Length Range</h5>
  <div class="form-group row">
    <label for="minPmBp" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Min</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="minPmBp" name="minPmBp" value="22">
    </div>
    <label for="maxPmBp" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Max</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="maxPmBp" name="maxPmBp" value="28">
    </div>
  </div><br/>
  <h5>Amplicon Length Range</h5>
  <div class="form-group row">
    <label for="minAmpBp" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Min</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="minAmpBp" name="minAmpBp" value="300">
    </div>
    <label for="maxAmpBp" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Max</label>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="maxAmpBp" name="maxAmpBp" value="1000">
    </div>
  </div><br/>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mb-2">Find Primers</button>
</form>